nodes.text: An otherwise untitled game was to be made by LucasArts and Factor 5. The game would have starred the Wookiee Chewbacca as a mercenary and would have been set after Star Wars Episode III: Revenge of the Sith. However, it was cancelled under George Lucas' order. This game was also the reason why another game made by Factor 5, Star Wars: Dark Squadron, a spinoff of the Rogue Squadron series, was cancelled as well.
